        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1773985271
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12805#discussion_r2964081000\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Oh for this the <code>default</code> feature lives <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/4834727b169cda1db365007c3a2970482b99c8ac/crates/c-api/artifact/Cargo.toml#L36\">here</a> instead which includes <code>gc</code>, so I think it's reasonable to just from <code>[dependencies]</code></p>\n</blockquote>",
