    {
        "content": "<p>tolumide-ng created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12805#discussion_r2968650078\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thank you for your response @alexcrichton, I am missing part of your suggestion here. Do you mean removing <code>gc</code> as a default feature in' wasmtime/Cargo. toml' and adding <code>#[cfg(feature = \"gc\")]</code> to the affected parts?</p>\n</blockquote>",
